om: URL: http://www.pharmacists.ca/function/Subscriptions/ecps.cfm?link=eCPS_quikLink."[5] EMEA. European Medicines Agency "EPARs. European Union Public Assessment Reports. Available from: URL: http://www.ema.europa.eu/ema/index.jsp?curl=pages/includes/medicines/medicines_landingpage.jsp&mid."[6] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0[7] Smith DS, Fujimoto JM "Alterations produced by novobiocin during biliary excretion of morphine, morphine-3-glucuronide and other compounds." J Pharmacol Exp Ther 188 (1974): 504-15', 1767369485);
